    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1872-06-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1872-06-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="5" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d5">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Record of the proceedings of the tribunal of
                                arbitration at the fourth conference held at Geneva, in Switzerland,
                                on the</hi> 17<hi rend="italic">th day of June</hi>, 1872.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>Geneva,
                                Switzerland</placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian" when="1872-06-17">June 17,
                                1872</date>.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The conference was held pursuant to adjournment. All the arbitrators were
                            present.</p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="margin">Adjournment.</seg> Mr. J. C. Bancroft Davis and Lord
                            Tenterden attended the conference as agents of the United States and Her
                            Britannic Majesty, respectively.</p>
                <p>The protocol of the last conference was read and approved, and was signed
                            by the president and secretary of the tribunal and the agents of the two
                            governments.</p>
                <p>Mr. Bancroft Davis stated that he was still without definite instructions
                            from his Government regarding the request of the British agent for
                            adjournment, and suggested a further adjournment of the tribunal until
                            Wednesday, the nineteenth instant.</p>
                <p>Lord Tenterden said that he could make no objection. The conference was
                            then adjourned to Wednesday, the 19th instant, at 2 o’clock.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>FREDERICK SCLOPIS.</item>
                            <item>J. C. BANCROFT DAVIS.</item>
                            <item>TENTERDEN.</item>
                            <item>ALEX. FAVROT, <hi rend="italic">Secretary</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
